The paper deals with image deconvolution, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves the use of fast Fourier transform (FFT) and iterative methods, which are common in information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and signal processing (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
